The paper deals with face recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The use of 3D models and deep learning methods suggests that the paper may also fall under graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM). The virtual synthesis approach involves generating synthetic data, which could be related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG).
